<h3>Welcome to the Latest and Greatest Skydiving Gear Resale Store</h3>
<p>We give you the tools to sell, buy, and look up skydiving gear</p>
</div>
<%= yield %>

<footer style="position:relative ; top: 100px; left: 300px; width: 600px; text-align: center;"> 
  <p style="font-size: 8pt;">* We have not been open since 1965, I just thought it sounded cool...Also we can only garuntee you we can help you keep feeling alive, not actually stay alive. Skydiving can be dangerous. Duh.</p>
